             were indicted for <rs id="t17980523-11-off55" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980523-11-off55" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980523-11-off55" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980523-11-victim134" type="victimName">
                           Ann 
                           Beaford
                        <interp inst="t17980523-11-victim134" type="surname" value="Beaford"></interp>
